{"tid":109024,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"溝女就同買鞋一個原理，一定要買新鞋","createTime":"2017-02-05T16:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T07:59:40.000Z","uid":54581,"like":46,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0a56183ebe81758ce8bbccf3bd9a7645cd42ad","tid":109024,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"女友就好似鞋咁<br />\n<br />\n你係第一手用家，自自然然錫到佢燶，幫佢keep幫佢保養，咩好野都俾晒佢<br />\n<br />\n佢要鞋油你買，佢要馬毛掃你買，佢貪靚要黑變啡打蠟，你都捨得俾佢，縱容佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反，你千金買對爛鞋番來，未用已經有一個二個洞係到，又俾人着到打晒摺<br />\n<br />\n塞對腳入對鞋到，發現個底銀住銀住，腳側位又鬆到咩咁<br />\n<br />\n咁係因為佢鞋邊已經俾上一手對腳着到闊晒，而鞋墊又經已適應左上一手用家對家<br />\n<br />\n你注定 <del><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌</span></del> 着得唔舒服"},{"pid":"6370665178677d87b4acf62eb9d701810ea39d1e","tid":109024,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531beb75c921938c7eaa5670adfdd28751a73e67","tid":109024,"uid":20087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"等睇公廁狗公話你物化女性<br />\n話你青頭仔"},{"pid":"7578308083b637f1bd96b4f24a9fff03ad35bdb6","tid":109024,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"物化女性<br />\n死青頭仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e4f7e7e3cae254cc23518523827a4ee494e4c0","tid":109024,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女友就好似鞋咁<br />\n<br />\n你係第一手用家，自自然然錫到佢燶，幫佢keep幫佢保養，咩好野都俾晒佢<br />\n<br />\n佢要鞋油你買，佢要馬毛掃你買，佢貪靚要黑變啡打蠟，你都捨得俾佢，縱容佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反，你千金買對爛鞋番來，未用已經有一個二個洞係到，又俾人着到打晒摺<br />\n<br />\n塞對腳入對鞋到，發現個底銀住銀住，腳側位又鬆到咩咁<br />\n<br />\n咁係因為佢鞋邊已經俾上一手對腳着到闊晒，而鞋墊又經已適應左上一手用家對家<br />\n<br />\n你注定 <del><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌</span></del> 着得唔舒服</blockquote><br />\n我覺得無乜所謂，不過亦因此要好好珍惜女朋友，真心覺得有你講既野係幾生修來，毒撚中做好人都會有人欣賞"},{"pid":"5ec3040b55add873a7443040e5be93decbf0eabe","tid":109024,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0e151d6a075e2b2dbcb61f73915523b93a6bce","tid":109024,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d2ee2b2a25c906c7ebf8c3b8b7ae1a90df09c3c8","tid":109024,"uid":23343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"岩啊屌"},{"pid":"dc25685f06be6c64bc3766f84e559de28fd2a660","tid":109024,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多新鞋"},{"pid":"d694c40edfff17252594e5ad5d0bc3fc00ca5aec","tid":109024,"uid":48189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04d9176a0ae4af27241e2988572ff6fcc41c681d","tid":109024,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錢買</blockquote><br />\n買對新淨波鞋<br />\n<br />\n好過殘舊皮鞋"},{"pid":"1f83a8af29bbcd9cd8dda985834b9b845bed6420","tid":109024,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"所以讀書拍到結個d最好"},{"pid":"52e58cdfd5247a29f92ac2551bad1406f5352357","tid":109024,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"搵男朋友就好似買手袋一樣<br />\n一定要全新 唔要display<br />\n咁多錢係手去買個手袋寧願"},{"pid":"cb6300daf51ed24e39f590d7a78b0a3387833075","tid":109024,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵男朋友就好似買手袋一樣<br />\n一定要全新 唔要display<br />\n咁多錢買個手袋寧願訂都唔會要display<br />\n啱唔啱? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"71ae4db2ada0e691510973e711d20eb1dcf69ff4","tid":109024,"uid":57414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"你睇下其他地區幾多人冇鞋著先得架<br />\n有鞋你著咪好咯"},{"pid":"6238fabe7455e5bc56c0c74893ebc284e947f892","tid":109024,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"咁我祝樓豬搵到個處女做女朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8b87c90bfac64b2983469fef2134710cc4cf7d","tid":109024,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你睇下其他地區幾多人冇鞋著先得架<br />\n有鞋你著咪好咯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992fcfc21607c273766f602c24ff1c1b2ed99f65","tid":109024,"uid":32842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你睇下其他地區幾多人冇鞋著先得架<br />\n有鞋你著咪好咯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔爭氣地笑咗"},{"pid":"f44392e6139d83b3cc80617b237f396a72120400","tid":109024,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"淨係鍾意著新鞋，著到舊就唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679ece2ed215ff2a73a324e1b36155f5e1199330","tid":109024,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你睇下其他地區幾多人冇鞋著先得架<br />\n有鞋你著咪好咯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔爭氣地笑咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" clas